나의 답  
def solution(n):  
    li = []  
    for i in str(n):  
        li.append(int(i))  
    answer = sum(li)  
    return answer  

print(solution(123))
print(solution(987))

해설 답  
def solution(n):  
    answer = 0  
    while n > 0:  
        answer += n % 10  
        n //= 10  
    return answer  

print(solution(123))
print(solution(987))

내가 좀 특이하게 푼 것 같다. 평범하게 풀어보자!
